317]]||{{ru|GEO}}||[[Kingsholm Stadium|Kingsholm]], [[Gloucester]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|20 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|NZL}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#New Zealand vs Argentina|26\u201316]]||{{ru|ARG}}||[[Wembley Stadium]], [[London]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|24 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|NZL}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#New Zealand vs Namibia|58\u201314]]||{{ru|NAM}}||[[Olympic Stadium (London)|Olympic Stadium]], [[London]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|25 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|ARG}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#Argentina vs Georgia|54\u20139]]||{{ru|GEO}}||[[Kingsholm Stadium|Kingsholm]], [[Gloucester]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|29 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|TON}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#Tonga vs Namibia|35\u201321]]||{{ru|NAM}}||[[Sandy Park]], [[Exeter]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|2 October 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|NZL}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#New Zealand vs Georgia|43\u201310]]||{{ru|GEO}}||[[Millennium Stadium]], [[Cardiff]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|4 October 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|ARG}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#Argentina vs Tonga|45\u201316]]||{{ru|TON}}||[[Leicester City Stadium]], [[Leicester]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|7 October 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|NAM}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#Namibia vs Georgia|16\u201317]]||{{ru|GEO}}||[[Sandy Park]], [[Exeter]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|9 October 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|NZL}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#New Zealand vs Tonga|47\u20139]]||{{ru|TON}}||[[St. James' Park]], [[Newcastle upon Tyne|Newcastle]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|11 October 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|ARG}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#Argentina vs Namibia|64\u201319]]||{{ru|NAM}}||[[Leicester City Stadium]], [[Leicester]]\n|}\n\n===Pool D=