ch Rugby Federation|France]])\n}}\n----\n{{rugbybox\n|date=18 October 2015\n|time=16:00 [[British Summer Time|BST]] ([[UTC+01]])\n|home={{ru-rt|AUS}}\n|score=[[2015 Rugby World Cup knockout stage#Australia vs Scotland|35\u201334]]\n|report=[http://www.rugbyworldcup.com/news/115493 Report]\n|away={{ru|SCO}}\n|try1=[[Adam Ashley-Cooper|Ashley-Cooper]] 9' m<br />[[Drew Mitchell|Mitchell]] (2) 30' m, 43' c<br />[[Michael Hooper (rugby union)|Hooper]] 40' m<br />[[Tevita Kuridrani|Kuridrani]] 64' c\n|con1=[[Bernard Foley|Foley]] (2/5) 44', 65'\n|pen1=[[Bernard Foley|Foley]] (2/2) 54', 80'\n|try2=[[Peter Horne|Horne]] 18' c<br />[[Tommy Seymour|Seymour]] 59' m<br />[[Mark Bennett (rugby union, born 1993)|Bennett]] 74' c\n|con2=[[Greig Laidlaw|Laidlaw]] (2/3) 19', 75'\n|pen2=[[Greig Laidlaw|Laidlaw]] (5/5) 14', 21', 34', 47', 69'\n|stadium=[[Twickenham Stadium]], [[London]]\n|attendance=77,110\n|referee=[[Craig Joubert]] ([[South African Rugby Union|South Africa]])\n}}\n\n===Semi-finals===\n{{rugbybox\n|date=24 October 2015\n|time=16:00 [[British Summer Time|BST]] ([[UTC+01]])\n|home={{ru-rt|RSA}}\n|score=[[2015 Rugby World Cup knockout stage#South Africa vs New Zealand|18\u201320]]\n|report=[http://www.rugbyworldcup.com/news/117722 Report]\n|away={{ru|NZL}}\n|pen1=[[Handr\u00e9 Pollard|Pollard]] (5/5) 3', 11', 21', 39', 58'<br />[[Pat Lambie|Lambie]] (1/1) 69'\n|try2=[[Jerome Kaino|Kaino]] 6' c<br />[[Beauden Barrett|Barrett]] 52' c\n|con2=[[Dan Carter|Carter]] (2/2) 9', 53'\n|pen2=[[Dan Carter|Carter]] (1/2) 60'\n|drop2=[[Dan Carter|Carter]] 46'\n|stadium=[[Twickenham Stadium]], [[London]]\n|attendance=80,090\n|referee=[[J\u00e9r\u00f4me Garc\u00e8s]] ([[French Rugby Federation|France]])\n}}\n----\n{{rugbybox\n|date=25 October 2015\n|time=16:00 [[Greenwich Mean Time|GMT]] ([[UTC+00]])\n|home={{ru-rt|ARG}}\n|score=[[2015 Rugby World Cup knockout stage#Argentina vs Australia|15\u201329]]\n|report=[http://www.rugbyworldcup.com/news/118584 Report]\n|away={{ru|AUS}}\n|pen1=[[