gia|16\u201317]]||{{ru|GEO}}||[[Sandy Park]], [[Exeter]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|9 October 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|NZL}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#New Zealand vs Tonga|47\u20139]]||{{ru|TON}}||[[St. James' Park]], [[Newcastle upon Tyne|Newcastle]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|11 October 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|ARG}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool C#Argentina vs Namibia|64\u201319]]||{{ru|NAM}}||[[Leicester City Stadium]], [[Leicester]]\n|}\n\n===Pool D===\n[[File:Ireland vs Canada 2015 RWC (3).jpg|thumb|Ireland beat Canada 50\u20137 at the Millennium Stadium in Cardiff.]]\n{{Main article|2015 Rugby World Cup Pool D}}\n{{2015 Rugby World Cup Pool D}}\n\n{| style=\"width:100%\" cellspacing=\"1\"\n|-\n!width=15%|\n!width=25%|\n!width=10%|\n!width=25%|\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|19 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|IRE}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool D#Ireland vs Canada|50\u20137]]||{{ru|CAN}}||[[Millennium Stadium]], [[Cardiff]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|19 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|FRA}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool D#France vs Italy|32\u201310]]||{{ru|ITA}}||[[Twickenham Stadium]], [[London]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|23 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|FRA}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool D#France vs Romania|38\u201311]]||{{ru|ROM}}||[[Olympic Stadium (London)|Olympic Stadium]], [[London]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|26 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|ITA}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool D#Italy vs Canada|23\u201318]]||{{ru|CAN}}||[[Elland Road]], [[Leeds]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|27 September 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|IRE}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool D#Ireland vs Romania|44\u201310]]||{{ru|ROM}}||[[Wembley Stadium]], [[London]]\n|- style=font-size:90%\n|align=right|1 October 2015||align=right|{{ru-rt|FRA}}||align=center|[[2015 Rugby World Cup Pool D#France vs Canada|41\u20