an Rugby Union|Australia]])\n}}\n----\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=22 October 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|ARG}}\n|score=50\u20133\n|away={{Ru|ROM}}\n|try1=[[Mart\u00edn Gait\u00e1n|Gait\u00e1n]]<br />[[Juan Mart\u00edn Hern\u00e1ndez|Hern\u00e1ndez]] (2)<br />[[Manuel Contepomi|M. Contepomi]]<br />[[Nicolas Fern\u00e1ndez Miranda|N. Fern\u00e1ndez Miranda]]<br />[[Pablo Bouza|Bouza]] (2)\n|con1=[[Juan Fern\u00e1ndez Miranda|J. Fern\u00e1ndez Miranda]] (4)<br />[[Gonzalo Quesada|Quesada]] (2)\n|pen1=[[Juan Fern\u00e1ndez Miranda|J. Fern\u00e1ndez Miranda]]\n|pen2=[[Ionut Tofan]]\n|stadium=[[Sydney Football Stadium|Aussie Stadium]], Sydney\n|attendance=33,673\n|referee=[[Chris White (referee)|Chris White]] ([[Rugby Football Union|England]])\n}}\n----\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=25 October 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|AUS}}\n|score=142\u20130\n|away={{Ru|NAM}}\n|try1=[[Chris Latham (rugby player)|Latham]] (5)<br />[[David Lyons (rugby union, born 1980)|Lyons]]<br />[[Stirling Mortlock|Mortlock]]<br />[[Lote Tuqiri|Tuqiri]] (3)<br />[[Try (rugby)|Penalty try]]<br />[[Mat Rogers|Rogers]] (2)<br />[[Jeremy Paul|Paul]]<br />[[Matt Giteau|Giteau]] (3)<br />[[Nathan Grey (rugby union)|Grey]]<br />[[Morgan Turinui|Turinui]] (2)<br />[[Matt Burke|Burke]]<br />[[John Roe (rugby union)|Roe]]\n|con1=[[Mat Rogers|Rogers]] (16)\n|stadium=[[Adelaide Oval]], Adelaide\n|attendance=28,196\n|referee=[[Jo\u00ebl Jutge]] ([[French Rugby Federation|France]])\n}}\n''Largest winning margin in [[Rugby World Cup]] history.''\n----\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=26 October 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|ARG}}\n|score=15\u201316\n|away={{Ru|IRE}}\n|pen1=[[Gonzalo Quesada|Quesada]] (3)\n|drop1=[[Gonzalo Quesada|Quesada]]<br />[[Ignacio Corleto|Corleto]]\n|try2=[[Alan Quinlan|Quinlan]]\n|con2=[[David Humphreys (rugby player)|Humphreys]]\n|pen2=[[David Humphreys (rugby player)|Humphreys]]<br />[[Ronan O'Gara|O'Gara]] (2)\n|stadium=[[Adelaide Oval]], Adelaide\n|attendance=30,203\n|referee=[[Andr\u00e9 Watson]] ([[South African Rugby Union|South Africa]])\n}