 referee)|Andrew Cole]] ([[Australian Rugby Union|Australia]])\n}}\n----\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=29 October 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|CAN}}\n|score=24\u20137\n|away={{Ru|TGA}}\n|try1=[[Sean Fauth|Fauth]]<br />[[Aaron Abrams (rugby union)|Abrams]]\n|con1=[[James Pritchard (rugby)|Pritchard]]\n|pen1=[[Bob Ross (rugby union footballer)|Ross]] (4)\n|try2=[[Benhur Kivalu|Kivalu]]\n|con2=[[Pierre Hola|Hola]]\n|stadium=[[WIN Stadium]], [[Wollongong]]\n|attendance=15,630\n|referee=[[Alain Rolland]] ([[Irish Rugby Football Union|Ireland]])\n}}\n----\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=2 November 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|NZL}}\n|score=53\u201337\n|away={{Ru|WAL}}\n|try1=[[Joe Rokocoko|Rokocoko]] (2)<br />[[Leon MacDonald|MacDonald]]<br />[[Ali Williams|Williams]]<br />[[Doug Howlett|Howlett]] (2)<br />[[Carlos Spencer|Spencer]]<br />[[Aaron Mauger|Mauger]]\n|con1=[[Leon MacDonald|MacDonald]] (5)\n|pen1=[[Leon MacDonald|MacDonald]]\n|try2=[[Mark Taylor (Welsh rugby player)|Taylor]]<br />[[Sonny Parker (rugby union)|Parker]]<br />[[Colin Charvis|Charvis]]<br />[[Shane Williams|S. Williams]]\n|con2=[[Stephen Jones (rugby player)|S. Jones]] (4)\n|pen2=[[Stephen Jones (rugby player)|S. Jones]] (3)\n|stadium=Stadium Australia, Sydney\n|attendance=80,012\n|referee=[[Andr\u00e9 Watson]] ([[South African Rugby Union|South Africa]])\n}}\n\n==Knockout stage==\n{{Round8-with third\n<!--Date\u2013Place|Team 1|Score 1|Team 2|Score 2 -->\n<!-- quarter-finals -->\n|8 November \u2013 [[Docklands Stadium|Melbourne]]|'''{{Ru|NZL}}'''|'''29'''|{{Ru|RSA}}|9\n|8 November \u2013 [[Lang Park|Brisbane]]|'''{{Ru|AUS}}'''|'''33'''|{{Ru|SCO}}|16\n|9 November \u2013 [[Docklands Stadium|Melbourne]]|'''{{Ru|FRA}}'''|'''43'''|{{Ru|IRE}} |21\n|9 November \u2013 [[Lang Park|Brisbane]]|'''{{Ru|ENG}}'''|'''28'''|{{Ru|WAL}}|17\n<!-- semi-finals -->\n|15 November \u2013 [[Stadium Australia|Sydney (Telstra)]]|{{Ru|NZL}}|10|'''{{Ru|AUS}}'''|'''22'''\n|16 November \u2013 [[Stadium Australia|Sydney (Telstra)]]|{{Ru|FRA}}|7|'''{{Ru|ENG}}'''|'''24'''\