eto|Corleto]]\n|try2=[[Alan Quinlan|Quinlan]]\n|con2=[[David Humphreys (rugby player)|Humphreys]]\n|pen2=[[David Humphreys (rugby player)|Humphreys]]<br />[[Ronan O'Gara|O'Gara]] (2)\n|stadium=[[Adelaide Oval]], Adelaide\n|attendance=30,203\n|referee=[[Andr\u00e9 Watson]] ([[South African Rugby Union|South Africa]])\n}}\n----\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=30 October 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|NAM}}\n|score=7\u201337\n|away={{Ru|ROM}}\n|try1=[[Eben Isaacs|Isaacs]]\n|con1=[[Emile Wessels|Wessels]]\n|try2=[[Augustin Petrichei|Petrichei]]<br />[[Lucian Sirbu|Sirbu]]<br />[[George Chiriac|Chiriac]]<br />[[Ioan Teodorescu|Teodorescu]]<br />[[Cristian Sauan|Sauan]]\n|con2=[[Ionut Tofan|Tofan]] (3)\n|pen2=[[Ionut Tofan|Tofan]] (2)\n|stadium=[[York Park]], [[Launceston, Tasmania|Launceston]]\n|attendance=15,457\n|referee=[[Peter Marshall (rugby referee)|Peter Marshall]] ([[Australian Rugby Union|Australia]])\n}}\n----\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=1 November 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|AUS}}\n|score=17\u201316\n|away={{Ru|IRE}}\n|try1=[[George Smith (rugby player)|Smith]]\n|pen1=[[Elton Flatley|Flatley]] (3)\n|drop1=[[George Gregan|Gregan]]\n|try2=[[Brian O'Driscoll|O'Driscoll]]\n|con2=[[Ronan O'Gara|O'Gara]]\n|pen2=[[Ronan O'Gara|O'Gara]] (2)\n|drop2=[[Brian O'Driscoll|O'Driscoll]]\n|stadium=Docklands Stadium, Melbourne\n|attendance=54,206\n|referee=[[Paddy O'Brien (rugby referee)|Paddy O'Brien]] ([[New Zealand Rugby Union|New Zealand]])\n}}\n\n===Pool B===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!width=165|Team\n!width=40|Pld\n!width=40|W\n!width=40|D\n!width=40|L\n!width=40|PF\n!width=40|PA\n!width=40|BP\n!width=40|Pts\n|- bgcolor=\"#ccffcc\"\n|align=left|{{Ru|FRA}}\n|4||4||0||0||204||70||4||'''20'''\n|- bgcolor=\"#ccffcc\"\n|align=left|{{Ru|SCO}}\n|4||3||0||1||102||97||2||'''14'''\n|-\n|align=left|{{Ru|FIJ}}\n|4||2||0||2||98||114||2||'''10'''\n|-\n|align=left|{{Ru|USA}}\n|4||1||0||3||86||125||2||'''6'''\n|-\n|align=left|{{Ru|JPN}}\n|4||0||0||4||79||163||0||'''0'''\n|}\n\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=1