ck Hougaard|Hougaard]]<br />[[Juan Smith|Smith]]<br />[[Ashwin Willemse|Willemse]]<br />[[Jaque Fourie|Fourie]]<br />[[Jaco van der Westhuyzen|Van der Westhuyzen]]<br />[[Neil de Kock|De Kock]]\n|con1=[[Derick Hougaard|Hougaard]] (5)<br />[[Louis Koen (rugby player)|Koen]] (2)\n|pen1=[[Derick Hougaard|Hougaard]]\n|drop1=[[Derick Hougaard|Hougaard]]\n|try2=[[Opeta Palepoi|Palepoi]]\n|con2=[[Earl Va'a|Va'a]]\n|pen2=[[Earl Va'a|Va'a]]\n|stadium=[[Suncorp Stadium]], [[Brisbane]]\n|attendance=48,496\n|referee=[[Chris White (referee)|Chris White]] ([[Rugby Football Union|England]])\n}}\n----\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=2 November 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|ENG}}\n|score=111\u201313\n|away={{Ru|URU}}\n|try1=[[Lewis Moody|Moody]]<br />[[Josh Lewsey|Lewsey]] (5)<br />[[Iain Balshaw|Balshaw]] (2)<br /> [[Mike Catt|Catt]] (2)<br />[[Andy Gomarsall|Gomarsall]] (2)<br />[[Dan Luger|Luger]]<br />[[Stuart Abbott|Abbott]]<br />[[Jason Robinson (rugby player)|Robinson]] (2)<br />[[Will Greenwood|Greenwood]]\n|con1=[[Paul Grayson (rugby player)|Grayson]] (11)<br />[[Mike Catt|Catt]] (2)\n|try2=[[Pablo Lemoine|Lemoine]]\n|con2=[[Juan Menchaca|Menchaca]]\n|pen2=[[Juan Menchaca|Menchaca]] (2)\n|stadium=[[Suncorp Stadium]], [[Brisbane]]\n|attendance=46,233\n|referee=[[Nigel Williams (rugby referee)|Nigel Williams]] ([[Welsh Rugby Union|Wales]])\n}}\n\n===Pool D===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!width=165|Team\n!width=40|Pld\n!width=40|W\n!width=40|D\n!width=40|L\n!width=40|PF\n!width=40|PA\n!width=40|BP\n!width=40|Pts\n|- bgcolor=\"#ccffcc\"\n|align=left|{{Ru|NZL}}\n|4||4||0||0||282||57||4||'''20'''\n|- bgcolor=\"#ccffcc\"\n|align=left|{{Ru|WAL}}\n|4||3||0||1||132||98||2||'''14'''\n|-\n|align=left|{{Ru|ITA}}\n|4||2||0||2||77||123||0||'''8'''\n|-\n|align=left|{{Ru|CAN}}\n|4||1||0||3||54||135||1||'''5'''\n|-\n|align=left|{{Ru|TGA}}\n|4||0||0||4||46||178||1||'''1'''\n|}\n\n{{Rugbybox\n|date=11 October 2003\n|home={{Ru-rt|NZL}}\n|score=70\u20137\n|away={{Ru|ITA}}\n|try1=[[Brad Tho